bnf: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.resource.cpu-vcores > mapreduce.map.cpu.vcores AND yarn.app.mapreduce.am.resource.cpu-vcores > mapreduce.reduce.cpu.vcores => mapreduce.job.ubertask.maxbytes != null
yarn.nodemanager.resource.count-logical-processors-as-cores = true => yarn.nodemanager.resource.cpu-vcores = number of logical CPUs * yarn.nodemanager.resource.pcores-vcores-multiplier
yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids in {rm1, rm2} => yarn.resourcemanager.webapp.address = rm1.resourcemanager.webapp.address | rm2.resourcemanager.webapp.address
yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids in {rm1, rm2} => yarn.resourcemanager.address = rm1.resourcemanager.address | rm2.resourcemanager.address
yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids in {rm1, rm2} => yarn.resourcemanager.scheduler.address = rm1.resourcemanager.scheduler.address | rm2.resourcemanager.scheduler.address
